---
---
<section id="packages" aria-labelledby="packages-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="packages-header">
      <div class="section-label" data-i18n="packages.label">Packages</div>
      <h2 class="section-title" id="packages-heading" data-i18n="packages.title">Productized. Predictable. Proven.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub" data-i18n="packages.sub">Scoped packages so you know exactly what you're getting — and what it costs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="platform-toggle" role="group" aria-label="Select platform">
      <button class="toggle-btn active" id="btn-shopify" aria-pressed="true">Shopify</button>
      <button class="toggle-btn" id="btn-woo" aria-pressed="false">WooCommerce</button>
    </div>

    <div class="packages-grid">
      <!-- Launch Sprint -->
      <article class="pkg-card reveal" aria-labelledby="pkg-1-name" data-popular-label="Most Popular">
        <h3 class="pkg-name" id="pkg-1-name" data-i18n="packages.pkg1.name">Launch Sprint</h3>
        <p class="pkg-for" data-i18n="packages.pkg1.for">For brands launching their first DTC store. Everything you need, nothing you don't.</p>
        <div class="pkg-price">$4,500<span style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--gray-2);font-weight:500;">+</span></div>
        <div class="pkg-timeline" id="pkg-1-timeline">5–7 day Shopify launch</div>
        <div class="pkg-divider"></div>
        <ul class="pkg-list" id="pkg-1-list" role="list">
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>Custom Shopify theme build</li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>Up to 5 pages (Home, PDP, Collection, About, Contact)</li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>Pixel setup (Meta, GA4)</li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>SEO foundation</li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>Performance optimization</li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>Welcome email flow</li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>2 rounds of revisions</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#cta" class="btn btn-outline" data-i18n="packages.cta">Book a Call</a>
      </article>

      <!-- Growth Sprint -->
      <article class="pkg-card featured reveal reveal-delay-1" aria-labelledby="pkg-2-name" data-popular-label="Most Popular">
        <h3 class="pkg-name" id="pkg-2-name" data-i18n="packages.pkg2.name">Growth Sprint</h3>
        <p class="pkg-for" data-i18n="packages.pkg2.for">For brands ready to turn their store into a revenue machine. Full stack execution.</p>
        <div class="pkg-price">$9,500<span style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--gray-2);font-weight:500;">+</span></div>
        <div class="pkg-timeline" id="pkg-2-timeline">Full build on Shopify in 10–14 days</div>
        <div class="pkg-divider"></div>
        <ul class="pkg-list" id="pkg-2-list" role="list">
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>Everything in Launch Sprint</li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>Brand identity &amp; packaging design</li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>Full pixel suite (Meta, GA4, TikTok)</li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>Post-purchase email + SMS flows</li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>Abandoned cart &amp; browse flows</li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>CRO audit &amp; UX sprint</li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>Loyalty &amp; referral setup</li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>30-day post-launch support</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#cta" class="btn btn-primary" data-i18n="packages.cta">Book a Call</a>
      </article>

      <!-- Growth Partner -->
      <article class="pkg-card reveal reveal-delay-2" aria-labelledby="pkg-3-name" data-popular-label="Most Popular">
        <h3 class="pkg-name" id="pkg-3-name" data-i18n="packages.pkg3.name">Ongoing Growth Partner</h3>
        <p class="pkg-for" data-i18n="packages.pkg3.for">For brands post-launch that want senior-level execution on a consistent basis.</p>
        <div class="pkg-price">$3,000<span style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--gray-2);font-weight:500;">/mo+</span></div>
        <div class="pkg-timeline" data-i18n="packages.pkg3.timeline">Ongoing — minimum 3 months</div>
        <div class="pkg-divider"></div>
        <ul class="pkg-list" role="list">
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span data-i18n="packages.pkg3.item1">Monthly CRO sprints</span></li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span data-i18n="packages.pkg3.item2">Email &amp; SMS optimization</span></li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span data-i18n="packages.pkg3.item3">Growth reporting &amp; analytics</span></li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span data-i18n="packages.pkg3.item4">Store updates &amp; new landing pages</span></li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span data-i18n="packages.pkg3.item5">Affiliate &amp; referral management</span></li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span data-i18n="packages.pkg3.item6">Priority response &amp; support</span></li>
          <li><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span data-i18n="packages.pkg3.item7">Quarterly strategy reviews</span></li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#cta" class="btn btn-outline" data-i18n="packages.cta">Book a Call</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
